data: unified by U+2BF4A (GZFY-00688) for IVS, irg47.

This character is a variant of U+632C 挬, and is not cognate with U+2BF4A (simplified form of U+3A6D 㩭).  The code chart glyph for U+2BF4A is incorrect, and does not match the source (Hànyǔ Fāngyán Dà Cídiǎn p. 5386), where the character is written ⿰扌学.
